                 to the Institute of Information Technology (IIT). The IIT was among a very few first institutes of the Pakistan
                  which offered a 4-year 8-semesters undergraduate Programmemes in Computer and Information Technology called BCIT.
                   Over the time it has undergone a number of revamps and currently Department of Information Technology is one of the
                    constituent departments of the recently established Faculty of
                 Engineering and Technology which offers a 4-year 8-semester undergraduate Programmemes BS Information Technology.
              </p> </div>

              <p>
