                   Technology Programmemes includes, in addition to fundamental core Information technology courses, a number of advanced
                    courses focusing on new emerging computing paradigms such as Mobile and Pervasive Computing, Cloud Computing, Information
                     security, smart technologies, human computer interface design (HCI), management of large scale IT infrastructure projects
